<br>
I think the truth behind all the euphorism is, that a lot of Mages realyl want to be like Wizards, more or less.<br>
Understablde to some degree, but not possible.<br>
You know, VI made some classes just too similiar and the closest classes to each other (regarding their role)are maybe Mage and Wizard.<br>
What makes us diferent for now from Mages is our abbility in burst damage, the role that was assumed for us by VI since the release of the game.<br>
Despite the fact that Lures, Draughts and the big bang Ice Comet are to a certain extinct the 'key nukes' of the wizard class and it is not at all cool to see that stuff going to a <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>pet</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, it is even more disturbing to see another class 'invading' 'our' niche - burst damage - via a 'npc' pet. As is clearly shown in this quote:<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>It is utterly hysterical to see the pet melee for a bit then double ice comet a GD giant and whack the SOB! MUAHAHAHAHAHAH!!! :&gt; <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Another fact is, that we have since the release of the game (thus pre kunark era) not seen a real upgrade to Ice Comet <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">damagewise.</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> Opposite, we received Ice spear, which has without doubt a better mana/dmg ratio, but smaller range and a 13 sec recast time. This makes Ice Comet still one of the most big punch Ice spells for us. I believe 99% of the Mages don't realize that. (Probably even VI doesn't realize that.)<br>
<br>
The further blurring of class lines won't help neither Wizards nor Mages in the long run.<br>
You can only hope, they will try to avoid such flaws in future games like EQ 2. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=121&stop=140>7</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=141&stop=160>8</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=161&stop=180>9</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=181&stop=200>10</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=201&stop=220>11</a> <b>12</b> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=241&stop=260>13</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=261&stop=280>14</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26582.topic&start=281&stop=300>15</a><a href=http://pu